            "title": "日股結束四連跌 反彈1286點或2.65%收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股終於結束之前連跌4個交易日的劣勢，全日高開高走，雖然重越5萬點後未能企穩，但仍顯著報升收市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/Financial_Markets_24198055000570.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/Financial_Markets_24198055000570.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經平均指數收報49823點，升1286點或2.65%；早市最高曾報50574點，低位49113點時仍升575點。</p>\n</div>",
